snippet.title: Pikmin 2 Infernal Edition Release Trailer (Pikmin 2 RomHack)
snippet.description:
Pikmin 2 Infernal Edition is like Pikmin 3 True Spice, it's Pikmin 2 on very hard mode :
60 pikmin max on the ground
Captains have 5 times less life
Pikmin do 3 times less damage
Enemies can eat 100 pikmin in 1 hit
Enemies and pellets give 1 pikmin seed
Day 1/3 shorter
10 days for finish

If you make videos with it put the link of my channel, thank you

Join my Discord for download
Discord : https://discord.gg/EzHHYZPSer

Thank you for watching the video, to help me continue subscribe to my Youtube channel
